  <div class="article-header">
        
   <h1>The No Excuses Take Your Lunch To Work Guide</h1>
	  <ul class="hmenu article-meta">
	    
	    
	  	<li class="first"><a href="http://www.mint.com/blog/author/guestblogger/" title="Posts by Guest Blogger">Guest Blogger</a> on 3/15/2008</li>
	  	<li><a href="http://www.mint.com/blog/saving/the-no-excuses-take-your-lunch-to-work-guide/#comments" class="comment-count">25 comments</a></li>
	  	  	<li><a href="?display=print" class="print">print</a></li>
  		<li>      <a class="random" href="http://www.mint.com/blog/credit-2/employment-credit-reports%e2%80%a6an-endangered-species-102011/">random</a>
         
      </li>
      <li>
        <iframe class="fb-like" src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mint.com%2Fblog%2Fsaving%2Fthe-no-excuses-take-your-lunch-to-work-guide%2F&amp;width=100&amp;layout=button_count&amp;show_faces=true&amp;action=like&amp;font&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;height=21" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowTransparency="true"></iframe> 
