    <img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/277baea5cfbae751398b1121bd89ee62?s=50&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D50&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-50 photo' height='50' width='50' /><cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.van-gogh-starry-night.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>oil paintings</a></cite></div><div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.mint.com/blog/saving/the-no-excuses-take-your-lunch-to-work-guide/comment-page-1/#comment-37951">916 days ago</a></div>
